race.comment: PAPER DOLL (14) was heavily supported here last start when missing by a head. Has her share of ability and is destined to break through soon but will need some luck from the wide alley. FORGING AHEAD (8) only warmed to his task late when resuming, closing off quickly from the back into a midfield finish. Better for the run will appreciate the extra ground. Don't take lightly. CROKER (6) couldn't quite live up to market expectation on debut but is a likely improver worth some thought. ATOMIC TIME (5) boasts a fitness edge and draws well. Have to keep safe.
